      <p class="p" style="margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;"><strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">三个关键认知：</strong></p><ol class="ol" style="padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">1. 框架比工具更持久——AI 迭代不会让框架过时</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">2. 与 AI 协作需要思维方式的转变，不只是技能习得</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">3. 你对 AI 输出负有最终责任，辨别和尽职不可省略</li></ol><p class="p" style="margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;"><em style="font-style: italic; font-size: inherit;"></em></p><ol class="ol" style="padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">1. <em style="font-style: italic; font-size: inherit;">Frameworks outlast tools — AI iteration won&#39;t make a framework obsolete</em></li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">2. <em style="font-style: italic; font-size: inherit;">Collaborating with AI requires a mindset shift, not just skill acquisition</em></li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">3. <em style="font-style: italic; font-size: inherit;">You bear final responsibility for AI output; discernment and diligence cannot be skipped</em></li></ol><hr class="hr" style="border-style: solid; border-width: 2px 0 0; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); -webkit-transform-origin: 0 0; -webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5); transform-origin: 0 0; transform: scale(1, 0.5); height: 0.4em; margin: 1.5em 0;"><p class="p" style="margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;"><strong style="color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">下一期预告 | Next Episode</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;">我们将探讨 AI 流利